metadata.description: "Lady Neuron" is a mesmerizing NFT artwork that draws inspiration from the intricate beauty of neurons in the human brain. This digital masterpiece captures the essence of a single neuron, showcasing its delicate, intertwined branches and vibrant electric pulses. With its vivid colors and intricate details, "Lady Neuron" invites viewers to contemplate the complex and mysterious workings of the human mind. This NFT celebrates the elegance and intricacy of neurons, offering a unique and captivating visual experience for art enthusiasts and neuroscience enthusiasts alike.
metadata.name: Lady neuron
